      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Welcome to Dead By Hunt.

    Dead By Hunt is a 1 vs 1 horror chase game.


    The
    Survivor wins by surviving until the timer reaches zero.

    The Killer wins
    by hitting the Survivor two times.


    Passages can only be used by the Survivor.

    The
    Killer can destroy passages.


    Power Ups can randomly appear during the match.


    Speed
    Boost:

    Increases movement speed for 5 seconds.

    Teleport:

    Can only
    be collected by the Survivor.

    Press E to teleport forward.


    Good luck
    and survive the hunt.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
